{"type":"answer","id":50189,"parentType":"question","parentId":11513,"uid":4630,"contents":"過去毛時代中共在非洲扶持代理人，就是在大街上和群眾聚會的時候演奏《東方紅》，強迫非洲人民學習毛澤東思想。<br>\n<br>\n以後西方自由世界和中共脫鉤，可以在機場和口岸演奏《榮光》、對中共陣營的遊客搞思想教育；不接受思想教育的人不準入境。<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/XG0epSf.gif\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-08-03","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":3}